                <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> "microplastic debris sorption of pollutants"@en ;
                rdfs:label "microplastic sorption process of pollutants"@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A synthetic polymer-based material sorption of pollutants that has as output some portion of synthetic polymer-based material that composes some microplastic debris particle with an increased level of pollutants as part (compared to levels prior to participating in that process)."@en ;
