                             "References to related processes can be added as needed." ;
                rdfs:label "modified natural polymer molecule"@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A synthetic polymer molecule that derives from a natural polymer molecule processed and altered through human intervention."@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


