                                  owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000264
                                ] ;
                rdfs:comment "We primarily focused on mineralization processes in relation to synthetic plastics, related polymers and items. Reference to such processes concerning plastics more in general, for instance in relation to natural plastics, or in relation to polymer-based materials can be added as needed."@en ;
                rdfs:label "plastic biomineralization process"@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A polymer biomineralization process that  applies to some biodegradable polymer molecules constituting some portion of biodegradable plastic"@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


