                                  owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000171
                                ] ;
                rdfs:comment "References to manufacturing processes of plastic objects made of specific type of plastics, such as recycled, virgin, biobased, and biodegradable can be added as needed."@en ;
                rdfs:label "plastic object manufacturing process"@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A manufacturing process of a piece of synthetic plastic that has a plastic object as the main output."@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


