                rdfs:comment "The focus is on synthetic plastics here."@en ;
                rdfs:label "plastic sorption process of pollutants"@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A synthetic polymer-based material sorption of pollutants that has as output some synthetic plastic with an increased level of pollutants as part (compared to levels prior to participating in that process)."@en ;
