                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A portion of polymer-based material that bears a disposition to be thermoset (thermosetting disposition)."@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo#ClimOO_0000252
:ClimOO_0000252 rdf:type owl:Class ;
                owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( :ClimOO_0000246
                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000091> ;
                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_06105002>
                                                           ]
                                                         ) ;
